This is an informal roadmap - no promise

ROADMAP

Version 2.0.3
- usual bug fixes and improvements
- parse correctly AS4_PATH (seems we do not when we should)

Version 2.0.4
- usual bug fixes and improvments
- implement generation and parsing of extended communities
  http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4360
- group update to up to maximum message size (4096 or more if negociated)
  http://www.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-idr-bgp-extended-messages-02.txt

LATER
- look what fun RFC we could implement from the list at 
  http://code.google.com/p/exabgp/wiki/RFC
